<head>
  <title>Hack Club Bank - ACH Transfer Confirmation Letter</title>
  <style>

    .container {
      font-size: 13.5pt;
      line-height: 1.15;
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 40pt;
      padding-right: 40pt;
      display: block;
    }

    .centerImage {
      position: relative;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
    }
    
    .bold {
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    body {
      margin: 8px;
      font-family: 'Arial';
    }

    a {
      color: #1155cc;
    }

    .auto-page-break { 
      page-break-before: auto;  
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <br />
  <div class="container">
    <br />
    <div style="height: 80px;">
        <p style="margin: 0; float: right; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.5">
          <span class="bold">Hack Club</span><br />
          <span style="white-space: nowrap;">8605 Santa Monica Boulevard #86294</span><br />
          West Hollywood, CA 90069<br />
          team@hackclub.com
        </p>
      <%= image_tag(wicked_pdf_asset_base64('hack_club_logo.png'), width: 156.6, height: 26.88, class: 'centerImage')%>
    </div>
    <br />
    <br />
    <br />
    <p style="margin-top: 2rem;"><%= Time.now.strftime("%B #{Time.now.day.ordinalize}, %Y") %></p>
    <br />
    <br />
    <p style="font-size: 12.5pt;"><span class="bold"><%= @event.name %> ACH Transfer to <%= @ach_transfer.recipient_name %></span></p>
    <br />

    <div style="line-height: 1.5;">
      <p>To whom it may concern,</p>
      <p><%= @ach_transfer.creator %></p>
      <p><%= @ach_transfer.payment_for %></p>
      <p><%= @ach_transfer.amount %></p>
      <p><%= @ach_transfer.status %></p>
      <p>
        This letter is to verify that EVENT NAME blah blah is acting as the nonprofit <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fiscal_sponsorship">fiscal sponsor</a> for <%= @event.name %>.
      </p>
      <p>
        We have established a restricted fund within our foundation to support their event and are
receiving funds on their behalf. The Hack Foundation is a 501(c)(3) public charity with the EIN 81-2908499.
      </p>
      <p>
        Please don't hesitate to contact me with any additional questions. I can be reached at <a href="mailto:michael@hackclub.com">michael@hackclub.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <br />
    <p>
      Best,
    </p>
    <%= image_tag(wicked_pdf_asset_base64('michael_signature.png'), width: 300, height: 73, dpi: 96) %>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5">
      Michael Destefanis<br />
      Director of Hack Club Bank<br />
      Hack Club
    </p>
    <br />
    <br />
    <p style="font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; color: #434343; position: fixed; bottom: 12px; width: 100%; white-space: nowrap;">
      By the students, for the students.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 10pt; color: #999999; position: fixed; bottom: 0px;">
      Hack Club is a 501(c)(3) public charity. Our nonprofit EIN is 81-2908499.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
